---
layout: "base"
title: "Durchatmen | PUK Zürich"
description: "Ein Moment Ruhe. Atemübung und Orientierung für Angehörige in belastenden Momenten."
permalink: "/tools/durchatmen/"
toolBackHref: "/"
toolBackLabel: "Zurück zur Startseite"
useSharedCSS: true
useNavJS: false
useToolCSS: true
bodyClass: "dark-tool"
breadcrumbs:
  - name: "Werkzeuge"
    url: "/werkzeuge/"
  - name: "Durchatmen"
    url: "/tools/durchatmen/"
---
{% block headCSS %}<!-- Durchatmen styles migrated to tools.css (P2.4) -->{% endblock %}
{% block nav %}
{% include "nav-tool.njk" %}
{% endblock %}
{% block content %}
<main class="breathe-wrap" id="main-content">
  <div class="tool-breadcrumb"><a href="/">Startseite</a><span class="sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span><a href="/werkzeuge/">Werkzeuge</a><span class="sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span><span>Durchatmen</span></div>
  <h1 class="breathe-title">Einen Moment.</h1>
  <p class="breathe-sub">Sie müssen gerade nichts entscheiden. Atmen Sie erst.</p>

  <div class="breathe-circle" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="breathe-label" id="breatheLabel">Einatmen</span>
  </div>

  <div class="breathe-steps">
    <div class="breathe-step"><span>4s</span>Einatmen</div>
    <div class="breathe-step"><span>4s</span>Halten</div>
    <div class="breathe-step"><span>6s</span>Ausatmen</div>
  </div>

  <div class="breathe-transition">
    <p class="breathe-transition-text">Wenn Sie bereit sind — ein kurzer Check:</p>
  </div>

  <div class="breathe-q">Brauchen Sie gerade Hilfe?</div>
  <div class="breathe-actions">
    <a href="tel:144" class="breathe-action breathe-action--emergency">Es besteht Gefahr — 144 anrufen</a>
    <a href="/tools/krisenplan/" class="breathe-action breathe-action--krisenplan">Krisenplan öffnen</a>
    <a href="/" class="breathe-action breathe-action--weiter">Ich schaue mich um → Orientierung</a>
  </div>
</main>
{% endblock %}
{% block footer %}
{% include "footer-medium.njk" %}
{% endblock %}
{% block scripts %}
<script>
var phases = [{text:'Einatmen',ms:4000},{text:'Halten',ms:4000},{text:'Ausatmen',ms:6000}];
var label = document.getElementById('breatheLabel');
var i = 0;
function cycle(){
  label.textContent = phases[i].text;
  setTimeout(function(){ i = (i+1)%3; cycle(); }, phases[i].ms);
}
cycle();
</script>
{% endblock %}
